title: The Rude Shipyard
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Small cafe and second-hand bookshop operating since 2009. Offers home style cooking with menu of mainly vegetarian dishes. Has soya and almond milk for drinks. Vegans could get a full breakfast, porridge with dried fruit and nuts, granola with dried fruit and nuts, lunch veggie burger, big salad plate, hummus sandwich. Usually at least one vegan cake on offer.
